{"tid":905262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩韓邊界崗哨傳槍響 南韓士兵頭部中彈身亡","createTime":"2018-11-17T03:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T05:37:56.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2c311de7087e2264708377e9234b606a961f2ac1","tid":905262,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:56:56.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一名駐守在兩韓邊界的南韓士兵，被發現頭部中彈，死在崗哨廁所中。<br />\n<br />\n根據《韓聯社》報導，南韓軍方說明，死者是一名年僅21歲的一等兵，8月被調派到該處。事件發生在當地時間昨日下午5點左右，該名士兵正負責夜間守望工作，資深軍官在聽到槍聲後趕到現場，發現他頭部中彈倒臥在廁所裡，並在送醫時死亡。<br />\n<br />\n軍方表示，案發至今沒有發現北韓有任何反常舉動，認為此案與北韓應無關聯，整起案件仍在調查中。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2615392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2615392&d=uYzQBpRLOc79lpwGqeW%2BxzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1dca4313\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2615392&h=468bbc86\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2615392</a>"},{"pid":"1c8804df44ec9c55846dcbd196094b1be190a891","tid":905262,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1582e1c0327f1ef00c72d20e3f5cee4cc094b842","tid":905262,"uid":4493,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:58:31.000Z","msg":"喺廁所入面九成九都係自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b98895d26ed15bb9f7444b479a18775e55aeead","tid":905262,"uid":4203,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:59:01.000Z","msg":"與神同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86116921f332d83320581767cec6e627e65a807","tid":905262,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"仲以為比北韓仔開槍打死"},{"pid"